Class CallableSimulateStayInAsset

    public class CallableSimulateStayInAsset
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.concurrent.Callable<java.lang.Double>
    The Class CallableSimulateStayInAsset. Used for simulating a single customer stay on a specific asset provided to meet a rental request . "This callable will simulate the presence of one customer in an asset. After the simulation is complete, a damage percentage to the asset is calculated and returned."
